            . I live in George-street, Minories. On the 5th of May, about half-past ten o'clock at night, I was walking along; I felt something - I turned and missed my handkerchief; I saw the prisoner a few yards off, throwing it down - I pursued him, and he was stopped; I had not lost sight of him - this is it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320517-216-person1672">
                  JOHN 
                  DAGLEY
               <interp inst="t18320517-216-person1672" type="surname" value="DAGLEY"></interp>
